course.subject: ENGG
course.name: Robotics Special Project: Unmanned Aerial Vehicle Competition 2024
course.description: There are various of Unmanned Aerial Vehicle Competition in the world. Student teams will design and manufacture the drones for tackling different missions and challenges which are provided by the organizer. Normally, a project report is required. Enrollment in the project course may require instructor's approval. May be graded PP.
